about.description:
Flexible and powerful tensor operations for readable and reliable code.
Supports numpy, pytorch, tensorflow, and others.
about.summary: A new flavour of deep learning operations.

name: einops
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "einops" %}
{% set version = "0.1.0" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 4fd64864fcb8159074da3213b9327c242536784416cbf423745ef8579850d30b

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.5
  run:
    - python >=3.5

test:
  imports:
    - einops
    - einops.layers

about:
  home: "https://github.com/arogozhnikov/einops"
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "A new flavour of deep learning operations."
  description: |
    Flexible and powerful tensor operations for readable and reliable code.
    Supports numpy, pytorch, tensorflow, and others.
  doc_url: "https://github.com/arogozhnikov/einops"
  dev_url: "https://github.com/arogozhnikov/einops"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - asford
